00:13:13.160 --> 00:13:15.430
<i>Mizuhara burada ne yapıyor?!</i>

00:13:15.810 --> 00:13:17.820
<i>Bekle, "Mizuhara" mı?</i>

00:13:17.820 --> 00:13:19.900
<i>Hayır, o Ichinose!</i>

